# Preparation

This takes the output of fragpipe when using any of the variants of the histonePTM_specLib workflow. This workflow performs a search with histone PTMs set as variable modifications. Importantly, it does not apply any filtering. The MSFragger output and spectral library are used as input to this filtering pipeline. It then outputs a filtered spectral library. 

